---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import { SITE } from '../config'
---

<Layout title="Norelis Monsalve — Product Manager">

  <section class="hero">
    <p class="label">Product Manager</p>
    <h1>I build digital products that turn complexity into clarity.</h1>
    <p class="bio">
      Strategic PM with 5+ years leading product discovery, UX, and delivery 
      across FinTech, EdTech, and SaaS. Focused on user-centric solutions 
      with measurable impact.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="work">
    <p class="label">Selected work</p>

    <a href="/work/onboarding" class="case-card">
      <span class="tag">EdTech · User activation</span>
      <h2>Reducing student onboarding time by 75% at Poliglota</h2>
      <p>Redesigned the enrollment flow with segmented paths and automated assessments, cutting activation time from 20 days to 5.</p>
      <div class="metrics">
        <span><strong>−75%</strong> onboarding time</span>
        <span><strong>20 → 5</strong> days</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/work/crm" class="case-card">
      <span class="tag">EdTech · Internal operations</span>
      <h2>CRM migration & sales process redesign at Poliglota</h2>
      <p>Led the migration from an internal CRM to HubSpot, aligning 4 teams and 40+ users while preserving 7 years of commercial data.</p>
      <div class="metrics">
        <span><strong>40+</strong> users migrated</span>
        <span><strong>&lt;1 week</strong> full adoption</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .nav-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; }

  .nav-link {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #666;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .nav-link:hover { color: #111; }

  .hero { margin-bottom: 4rem; }

  .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .bio {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #666;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .work { margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .work .label { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }

  .case-card {
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .case-card:hover { border-color: #999; }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #999;
    background: #f4f4f4;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .case-card h2 {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .case-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .metrics { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .metrics span { font-size: 13px; color: #999; }
  .metrics strong { color: #111; font-weight: 500; }

  footer {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  footer a { font-size: 14px; color: #666; transition: color 0.15s; }
  footer a:hover { color: #111; }
</style>